{"TopicId":148903,"ForumId":81,"TopicTitle":"Any plan for construct camera redux control?","CreatedByName":"Cheesemass","CreatedById":169531,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T08:08:42Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Cheesemass","CreatedById":169531,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-29T08:08:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlaying this game on Xbox is a challenge in and of itself. \u00A0The game could really fly if the controls merge better. \u00A0I\u0027m left wondering though if in the hangers - will the camera control ever be simplified?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA simple strafing movement in conjunction with the zoom would go a long way...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-30T15:50:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCamera translation is available in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022SpacePlane Hangar\u0022\u003ESPH\u003C/abbr\u003E (but not \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E). I believe the xbox control for this is:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ctable border=\u00220\u0022 cellpadding=\u00220\u0022 cellspacing=\u00220\u0022 style=\u0022box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(39, 42, 52); font-family: \u0026quot;Helvetica Neue\u0026quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 237pt;\u0022 width=\u0022316\u0022\u003E\u003Ctbody style=\u0022box-sizing: border-box;\u0022\u003E\u003Ctr style=\u0022box-sizing: border-box; height: 15pt;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ctd height=\u002220\u0022 style=\u0022box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px rgb(0, 0, 0); height: 15pt; background-color: rgb(189, 215,